SummaryEnglish: Animated comedy about two strange maggots, Red and Yellow, who live under the grill of a sewer drain where people pay little attention. In this secret place, they relish in the things that people throw in the sewer, like chewed up bubble gum, melted ice cream, coins, rings, you name it. They sometimes get into trouble, play happily and squabble over possession of these things.

1.SummaryEnglish: In this movie sequel to the hit series, Chuck returns home and talks to a reporter about life on the island with zany larva pals Red and Yellow.

52.TitleEnglish: A Day in The Life of Larva
